<FIRST>r p BC-INDIANAAt-A-Glance     05-03 0205</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-INDIANA At-A-Glance,200</SECOND>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Here, at a glance, are the methods for picking delegates from <LOCATION> Indiana </LOCATION> to attend the 1988 Democratic and Republican national conventions this summer.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>DEMOCRATS</HEAD>
<TEXT>
