'' said <PERSON> Maggie </PERSON> <PERSON> Thomas </PERSON>. Yet <PERSON> Collins </PERSON> said he left <LOCATION> Naperville </LOCATION> because he did n't want to further divide the parish, and retreated to <LOCATION> Crest </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Hill </LOCATION> to write his book.
